### ðŸ¥‡ #1: PDF Bank Statement to CSV Converter + Auto-Categorization

**Why This Wins:**
- âœ… **Massive Pain Point:** Banks lock historical data in PDFs
- âœ… **Market Differentiation:** Free converter + AI categorization = unique value prop
- âœ… **Viral Potential:** "Finally access your 7-year Chase history for free"
